title: HOUR 1- Sep 10, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 1- Sep 10, 2020
description:
Dan talks about the Chiefs being rubber stamped as a dynasty. Dan compares the Chiefs to the run of the Patriots and how close they came to not winning at least two of their Super Bowls. Dan says the Chiefs could have been eliminated early in the playoffs and was down in the Super Bowl; so hold off on calling them a dynasty.
